404
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:48,230
So it must be for love.

405
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,360
You came back for Beichuan.

406
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:53,290
I didn't come back for him.

407
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,440
Xining,

408
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:57,270
I read a book the other day,

409
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:59,170
and it said some really good things.

410
00:29:59,170 --> 00:30:00,570
It said that

411
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:03,120
a woman shouldn't imagine a man
as perfect,

412
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:05,570
because he can't be perfect in real life.

413
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:08,490
That would just put too much pressure
on him.

414
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:10,240
For a woman,

415
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,920
if she loves too intensely,

416
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:15,550
she becomes too sensitive.

417
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:17,960
Even the tiniest crack

418
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:20,200
gets magnified by her.

419
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,550
And what about men?

420
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:25,960
It's the same.

421
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:27,030
Think about it—

422
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:29,640
if a man treats you like a goddess—

423
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:32,410
but you're not actually a goddess

424
00:30:32,430 --> 00:30:34,070
and have so many flaws—

425
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:37,680
doesn't that make you exhausted
and under a lot of pressure?

426
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:40,030
And his love

427
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:42,480
will also be intense.

428
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:45,580
Then he'll become very sensitive.

429
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:47,310
Then

430
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,200
even the tiniest crack

431
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,740
will get magnified by him as well.

432
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,510
So are you saying

433
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:59,060
men and women

434
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,520
shouldn't love too intensely?

435
00:31:01,550 --> 00:31:02,270
No.

436
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:04,510
Then what are you saying?

437
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:07,640
Love is about managing

438
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:09,620
and exercising restraint.

439
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,110
Mr. Guo,

440
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:35,970
I believe this is my class.

441
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:37,070
Professor Xiang.

442
00:31:37,140 --> 00:31:38,160
Come here.

443
00:31:45,510 --> 00:31:46,160
Beichuan,

444
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:47,750
about the apartment,

445
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,860
I've always been grateful to you.

446
00:31:51,310 --> 00:31:51,960
Today,

447
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:54,200
they insisted I substitute for you.

448
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,740
I said I wouldn't come,

449
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,200
but everyone in our department

450
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,790
insisted.

451
00:31:59,970 --> 00:32:01,830
They said only my teaching skills

452
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,640
are on the same level as yours.

453
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:05,510
Mr. Guo,

454
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:07,700
you're substituting for me?

455
00:32:09,550 --> 00:32:10,400
I know about

456
00:32:11,010 --> 00:32:12,140
that thing of yours.

457
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,000
Others might think

458
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:16,450
it's kind of shady,

459
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,110
but to me,

460
00:32:18,340 --> 00:32:19,660
you're very brave

461
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,310
when it comes to love.

462
00:32:22,270 --> 00:32:25,130
I've always thought
you're a truly genuine person.

463
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:28,270
What thing?

464
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:31,340
How come I don't even know about this
myself?

465
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:36,400
Love in Partition Room.

466
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,330
Love in Partition Room?

467
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,930
Professor Xiang,
could you come out for a moment?

468
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,480
It's been a pleasure working with you.

469
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,550
Thank you.

470
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,750
I hope we can work together again.

471
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,590
Sure thing.

472
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:55,310
Take care, Mr. Liu.

473
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,030
Alright.

474
00:32:56,110 --> 00:32:56,720
Take care.

475
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:01,680
How is it?

476
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:03,880
How's the booth?

477
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:04,720
Look.

478
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:06,850
Ours is a step higher than the others'.

479
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:10,510
Normally, that would make it 5,000 yuan
more expensive,

480
00:33:10,510 --> 00:33:13,020
but I got it without adding a cent.

481
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:16,070
It was mainly because
your products are good.

482
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:17,480
The brand you represent is great.

483
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,590
That's why our products sell well.

484
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:21,350
That's why they gave us the best spot.

485
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:21,960
Right?

486
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:22,590
Alright, Jiuling.

487
00:33:22,590 --> 00:33:23,880
Stop praising me.

488
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:25,880
We're going to do better and better.

489
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:26,680
Right now,

490
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:28,480
I'm going to build my own brand.

491
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:30,750
I'm currently
looking for a factory location.

492
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:31,550
Don't worry.

493
00:33:32,130 --> 00:33:33,790
I'll work with you from now on.

494
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:36,400
Of course. We make such a great team.

495
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,200
That's right.

496
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:40,400
Beichuan,

497
00:33:40,790 --> 00:33:41,590
have a seat.

498
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,210
Mr. Zhong, what's going on?

499
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,940
I need to get back to class.

500
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,030
You should

501
00:33:49,330 --> 00:33:50,240
take a look at this first.

502
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:52,430
[Zhuohua]

503
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,280
Mr. Zhong,

504
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:23,489
I'm resigning.

505
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,550
Beichuan,

506
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,960
you're a young teacher
I personally selected.

507
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:32,710
I have

508
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:35,010
high expectations for you.

509
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:36,650
And now you're resigning?

510
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:38,400
You're not Yan Jun.

511
00:34:38,699 --> 00:34:40,560
You don't know how to do business.

512
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:43,389
Jobs are hard to find these days.

513
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:44,400
If you resign,

514
00:34:45,070 --> 00:34:46,270
how will you survive?

515
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,070
Mr. Zhong,

516
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,969
I think what you said about me is right.

517
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:01,030
I am indeed sometimes too rigid.

518
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:02,630
And as you said,

519
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:04,880
as a teacher,

520
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,960
it's not enough to just know my subject—

521
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:10,290
I should also know
how to deal with people.

522
00:35:12,550 --> 00:35:14,030
But to be honest,

523
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:17,860
I don't really want to learn that,

524
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:20,350
and I don't want to be too sophisticated.

525
00:35:20,350 --> 00:35:21,460
Can you forgive me?

526
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,240
Don't worry.

527
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:29,550
I'll submit a formal resignation

528
00:35:29,550 --> 00:35:31,360
to the department later,

529
00:35:33,190 --> 00:35:34,790
and I hope you'll approve it.

530
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:47,190
Downstairs are our summer items,

531
00:35:47,190 --> 00:35:49,110
and this is the fall collection.

532
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:51,150
But it's our best-selling item
in the store.

533
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:52,550
Do you have any in season?

534
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,480
In season?

535
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:53,920
Yes.

536
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:54,870
Well...

537
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:56,320
Mr. Yan.

538
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:57,720
Jiuling.

539
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:00,110
Well, Jiuling,

540
00:36:00,110 --> 00:36:01,550
could you go take a walk outside?

541
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:03,280
I need to have a word with Xining.

542
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,080
That won't do.

543
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:05,760
I'm staying with Xining.

544
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:07,670
Just sit down and say it.

545
00:36:07,890 --> 00:36:08,830
-I'm not an outsider.
-It's okay. Just say it.

546
00:36:08,830 --> 00:36:09,490
Just say it.

547
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:14,900
Have you seen this?

548
00:36:16,110 --> 00:36:16,630
No.

549
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:18,030
There's a page I folded the corner of.

550
00:36:18,030 --> 00:36:19,290
Open it and take a look.

551
00:36:23,730 --> 00:36:25,710
[Love in Partition Room]

552
00:36:24,250 --> 00:36:25,080
Tong Tong?

553
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,670
She published her work?

554
00:36:27,770 --> 00:36:28,830
You know Tong Tong?

555
00:36:29,570 --> 00:36:31,770
She used to pester Xiang Beichuan a lot.

556
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,420
What did she write?

557
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,710
How could she write such nonsense?

558
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:41,240
She included all of us in it.

559
00:36:42,030 --> 00:36:43,510
She even said
she's with Xiang Beichuan now

560
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:45,440
and that they're living together.

561
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,080
Let me see.

562
00:36:47,810 --> 00:36:49,590
"He gently took off my…"

563
00:36:50,970 --> 00:36:52,230
What is this? This kid.

564
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:54,090
Hugging and... kissing?

565
00:36:54,970 --> 00:36:56,890
She's just a kid.

566
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,710
Look at how she wrote about me.

567
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:01,140
It says I just want sex every night

568
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:03,440
and that I'm like a horny dog.

569
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:07,010
Good thing she didn't mention me.

570
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:10,480
"There's always an old woman
following the girl around..."

571
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,920
What is this?

